source.name: TradeStats Express
source.description: TradeStats Express provides statistics on U.S. merchandise trade at the national and state levels.  Data can also be displayed in maps, graphs, tables, or as exports, imports, and trade balances. Note: this does not include statistics on U.S. trade in services.
